<!doctype html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <meta name="robots" content="noindex" />
    <title>Alpha blog CMS</title>
    <style>
      .cms-writing-guide {
        position: fixed;
        right: 18px;
        bottom: 18px;
        z-index: 1000;
        width: min(360px, calc(100vw - 36px));
        max-height: 48vh;
        overflow: auto;
        border: 1px solid rgba(45, 56, 48, 0.14);
        border-radius: 14px;
        background: rgba(255, 255, 252, 0.92);
        box-shadow: 0 18px 44px rgba(20, 26, 22, 0.14);
        color: #1d241f;
        font-family:
          Inter, ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI",
          sans-serif;
        backdrop-filter: blur(16px) saturate(1.05);
      }

      .cms-writing-guide summary {
        cursor: pointer;
        padding: 12px 14px;
        font-weight: 760;
      }

      .cms-writing-guide[open] summary {
        border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(45, 56, 48, 0.1);
      }

      .cms-writing-guide div {
        padding: 12px 14px 14px;
        font-size: 13px;
        line-height: 1.55;
      }

      .cms-writing-guide p,
      .cms-writing-guide ul {
        margin: 0 0 10px;
      }

      .cms-writing-guide ul {
        padding-left: 18px;
      }

      .cms-writing-guide code {
        border-radius: 6px;
        padding: 1px 5px;
        background: #eef4ef;
        color: #245b47;
      }

      @media (max-width: 720px) {
        .cms-writing-guide {
          display: none;
        }
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body data-pagefind-ignore>
    <details class="cms-writing-guide">
      <summary>写作提示：优先使用 Insert</summary>
      <div>
        <p>正文编辑区会显示普通 Markdown/短代码文本，不会折叠成虚线组件块。尽量使用工具栏的 <code>Insert</code> 菜单，不要手写 HTML 标签。</p>
        <ul>
          <li>提示块：<code>:::callout</code></li>
          <li>折叠框：<code>:::details</code></li>
          <li>双列：<code>::::columns</code></li>
          <li>计划：<code>:::plan</code></li>
          <li>时间线：<code>:::timeline</code></li>
        </ul>
        <p>保存前看右侧预览；如果预览里还显示短代码，通常是缺少结尾的 <code>:::</code>。</p>
      </div>
    </details>
    <script is:inline>
      window.CMS_MANUAL_INIT = true;
    </script>
    <script is:inline src="https://unpkg.com/@sveltia/cms@0.167.3/dist/sveltia-cms.js"></script>
    <script is:inline src="/admin/cms.js"></script>
  </body>
</html>
